TANZANYA

825
00:44:54,002 --> 00:44:56,004
Her yer sessiz

826
00:44:56,046 --> 00:44:57,881
İNSAN YİYEN ASLAN:7

827
00:44:58,048 --> 00:45:00,050
Her şey

828
00:45:00,092 --> 00:45:01,134
Parlak

829
00:45:01,260 --> 00:45:03,220
Farkındayım

830
00:45:03,262 --> 00:45:05,389
Delice
Ama bu gece

831
00:45:06,390 --> 00:45:07,516
Biliyorum ki

832
00:45:09,393 --> 00:45:11,478
Noel

833
00:45:11,561 --> 00:45:12,688
Tatlı kedicik

834
00:45:12,729 --> 00:45:15,732
Bırak bizi gidelim

835
00:45:16,775 --> 00:45:18,819
Sen de uyu

836
00:45:18,902 --> 00:45:23,156
Sakin sakin

837
00:45:25,033 --> 00:45:27,119
